1> Align and SNP calling:

Example:

Pair-end:
./snpMap.pl -f align -in sample/test_R1.fastq sample/test_R2.fastq -t sample/ce10.fasta -config sample/snpmap.config 2> snpmap.align.log

Single-end:
./snpMap.pl -f align -in sample/test.fastq -t sample/ce10.fasta -config sample/snpmap.config 2> snpmap.align.log

2> Count SNP frequency in all samples, output to file gene.freq.txt.

Example:
./SnpMap.pl -f freq -d sample/snp
